## Color Tokens (Tailwind)

```typescript
// PRIMARY PALETTE (Production Spec)
colors: {
  lbta: {
    orange: '#F8A121',      // Primary accent, focus states, links
    red: '#F04E23',         // CTA buttons, urgency
    beige: '#F8E6BB',       // Warm background sections
    black: '#000000',       // Primary text
    white: '#FFFFFF',       // Pure white

    // LEGACY (backwards compatibility)
    primary: '#1A1A1A',     // Text primary
    secondary: '#6B6B6B',   // Text secondary
    coral: '#E8956F',       // Accent
    'coral-dark': '#D67D5A',
    bone: '#FDFCFA',        // Light background
    sand: '#F4EDE4',        // Warm neutral
    charcoal: '#2B2B2B',    // Dark text
  },
  vylo: {
    orange: '#F26522',      // VYLO sub-brand
  }
}
```

**Color Usage Rules:**
- Never use more than 3 colors in a single section
- Orange (#F8A121) for interactive elements and emphasis
- Red (#F04E23) ONLY for primary CTAs
- Beige (#F8E6BB) for warm, inviting sections
- Black/White for text and backgrounds

---

## Typography System

```typescript
fontFamily: {
  headline: ['Playfair Display', 'Georgia', 'serif'],
  body: ['Work Sans', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],
  serif: ['Playfair Display', 'Georgia', 'serif'],
  sans: ['Work Sans', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],
}

// NEVER USE: Space Grotesk, Inter, Roboto (causes accessibility bugs)
```

**Typography Scale:**
```
- Display:     clamp(48px, 9vw, 84px)  — Hero headlines only
- Headline:    clamp(40px, 6vw, 64px)  — Section titles
- Headline-md: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px)  — Subsection titles
- Headline-sm: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px)  — Card titles
- Subhead:     clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 32px) — Lead paragraphs
- Body-lg:     20px                     — Emphasis body
- Body:        18px                     — Standard body
- Body-sm:     16px                     — Small text
- Eyebrow:     11px (uppercase, 2px letter-spacing)
```

---

## Spacing System (12px Base Unit)

```typescript
spacing: {
  '15': '60px',    // 12 × 5
  '18': '72px',    // 12 × 6
  '20': '80px',    // Standard section gap
  '24': '96px',    // 12 × 8
  '30': '120px',   // Blueprint outer margins (desktop)
  '40': '160px',   // Section spacing medium
  '60': '240px',   // Section padding desktop
}
```

**Section Spacing Rules:**
```css
/* Mobile */
.section { padding: 80px 24px; }

/* Tablet */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .section { padding: 120px 48px; }
}

/* Desktop */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .section { padding: 160px 96px; }
}
```

