## Component Patterns

### Buttons
```tsx
// Primary CTA (Book Trial, Register)
<button className="
  inline-flex items-center justify-center
  bg-black text-white
  font-sans text-sm font-medium
  tracking-[2.5px] uppercase
  min-h-[48px] px-10 py-4
  rounded-[2px]
  transition-all duration-800 ease-cinematic
  hover:bg-lbta-orange hover:-translate-y-0.5
  focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-lbta-orange focus:ring-offset-2
">
  Book Trial
</button>

// Secondary (Learn More, Explore)
<button className="
  inline-flex items-center justify-center
  bg-transparent text-black
  border border-black/20
  font-sans text-sm font-medium
  tracking-[2.5px] uppercase
  min-h-[48px] px-10 py-4
  rounded-[2px]
  transition-all duration-800 ease-cinematic
  hover:border-black hover:-translate-y-0.5
  focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-lbta-orange focus:ring-offset-2
">
  Learn More
</button>
```

### Cards
```tsx
<div className="
  bg-white
  border border-black/6
  transition-all duration-1200 ease-cinematic
  shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.02),0_2px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.02),0_4px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.02)]
  hover:border-black/10 hover:-translate-y-1
  hover:shadow-[0_4px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03),0_8px_16px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03),0_16px_32px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)]
">
