## Data Management Rules

### Prices
```
✅ Prices ONLY in /pricing page
✅ Fetch from JSON or API
❌ NEVER hardcode prices in components
❌ NEVER duplicate prices across pages
```

### Dates/Schedules
```
✅ Dates can appear on schedule page, cards, and modules
✅ Use consistent date formatting: "January 6, 2026"
✅ Store in data/winter2026.json, data/fall2025.json
```

---

## SEO & Metadata

```tsx
// Every page must have metadata
export const metadata: Metadata = {
  title: 'Page Title | Laguna Beach Tennis Academy',
  description: 'Under 160 characters. Include location + key benefit.',
  keywords: 'tennis lessons Laguna Beach, [specific keywords]',
  openGraph: {
    title: 'Page Title | LBTA',
    description: 'Same as meta description',
    type: 'website',
    images: ['/images/og-image.jpg'],
  },
}
```

---

## HTML Standards

```html
<!-- Semantic structure REQUIRED -->
<main>
  <section aria-labelledby="section-title">
    <h2 id="section-title">Section Title</h2>
    <!-- Content -->
  </section>
</main>

<!-- Form accessibility -->
<label htmlFor="email">Email Address</label>
<input
  id="email"
  type="email"
  name="email"
  required
  aria-describedby="email-hint"
/>
<span id="email-hint">We'll never share your email.</span>

<!-- Image accessibility -->
<Image
  src="/image.webp"
  alt="Andrew Mateljan coaching a junior player on court 3"
  // Alt text: descriptive, under 125 chars, no "image of" prefix
/>
```

---

## Forbidden Patterns

### Copy/Messaging
```
❌ "Maximize", "boost", "elite", "world-class"
❌ "Sign up now!", "Don't miss out!", "Limited time!"
❌ Fake scarcity or urgency
❌ Generic marketing speak
❌ Exclamation points in headlines

✅ "Book a Trial", "Start Training", "Join the Community"
✅ Calm, confident, specific language
✅ Founder's authentic voice
```

### Code
```
❌ Inline event handlers (onclick="...")
❌ Removed focus outlines
❌ Images without alt text
❌ Horizontal scroll on mobile
❌ Animations without reduced-motion support
❌ Hardcoded prices outside /pricing
❌ Stock photos
❌ More than 11 colors
❌ Space Grotesk, Inter, Roboto fonts
```

---

## Testing Checklist (Every PR)

```markdown
## Performance
- [ ] Lighthouse ≥90 (Performance, Accessibility, Best Practices, SEO)
- [ ] LCP < 2.5s on 3G throttled
- [ ] CLS < 0.1
- [ ] No horizontal scroll at any breakpoint

## Accessibility
- [ ] 7:1 contrast ratio verified (WebAIM)
- [ ] Keyboard navigation complete
- [ ] Screen reader tested (VoiceOver/NVDA)
- [ ] Focus states visible
- [ ] Touch targets ≥48px on mobile

## Responsive
- [ ] Tested at 320px, 375px, 768px, 1024px, 1440px
- [ ] Images lazy-loaded below fold
- [ ] Text readable without zoom

## Brand
- [ ] Copy matches founder voice (calm, confident)
- [ ] No forbidden words/phrases
- [ ] Colors within palette
- [ ] Typography hierarchy correct
```

